<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Certificate of Completion</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
    .header { background-color: #0052cc; color: white; padding: 10px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
    .content { padding: 20px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 20px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #2684FF; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Certificate of Completion</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</p>
      <p>Congratulations on completing the <strong><%= courseName %></strong> course at Beks Coding Club Foundation Track!</p>
      <p>Your certificate is ready! Click the link below to download it:</p>
      <p><a href="<%= downloadLink %>" class="button">Download Your Certificate</a></p>
      <p>It was issued on <%= completionDate %>.</p>
      <p>We’re proud of your achievement and wish you success in your future endeavors.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>Beks Coding Club Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Beks Coding Club. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>